        "subject": "LU-2763 build: git commit fails to allow long Test-Paramters",
        "message": "LU-2763 build: git commit fails to allow long Test-Paramters\n\nWhile trying to a longer Test-Paramater I found I was\nunable to. The paramaters were a total of 120 chars or so.\nRegardless of any escaping I tried commits were failed\ntelling me my lines were over 70 chars long.\n\nIt was suggest that we use the commit-msg hook from Master.\n\nWith local testing it seems to work just fine.\n\nSigned-off-by: Keith Mannthey <keith.mannthey@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5e7c6dfe6f34340ba53e1c2439d2b454a786bc19\n"
